Stadium Ticket RESTful API for Linux/Unix

0.  To install prerequisites:

    apt install apache2-utils mariadb-server python3 python3-flask python3-pymysql python3-sqlalchemy	# Debian/Ubuntu
    dnf install apache2-utils mariadb python3 python3-flask python3-PyMySQL python3-sqlalchemy		# Fedora
    pkg install apache2-utils mariadb python3		# BSD/Illumos
    yum install apache2-utils mariadb python3		# CentOS/RHEL
    zypper install apache2-utils mariadb python3	# openSUSE/SLED/SLES
    ./install-prequisites

1.  To initialize database:

    mysql -p <schema.sql

2.  To run unit tests:

    ./test_tickets.py

3.  To start API:

    ./app.py

4.  To test API:

    ./test-app.sh

5.  To load test API:

    ./load-test.sh
